[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    910[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     metrics, and the model versions. Production runs each model
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    911[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     as a separate SageMaker training job, applies a quality gate
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    912[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     against the current production model, and atomically deploys
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    913[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     both behind the inference endpoint. The demo returns the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    914[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     trained objects directly.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    915[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
